```
=LEN(A2)-LEN(SUBSTITUTE(LOWER(A2), "x", ""))
```

We will place the results in new columns named “a”, “b”, …, “z” next to the original text column. After writing the formulas, we will save the workbook to the output directory and verify that the formulas are present.

